name: First Ever Meme Currency
description: KEKELS AS A MEME CURRENCY Kekels is a fictional currency of the satirical "Peopleâ€™s Republic of Kekistan," a meme-based "nation" from Reddit and 4chan. With a flag, "Cult of Kek," and Pepe the Frog, Kekistan parodies real countries. Kekels humorously represents value in this fictional world, with joking exchange rates like 1 Kekel = 0.1 EUR or 1 USD, but it has no real-world value.
